# Finite Sites Caddyfile for finite-lat-2 (dedicated sites box).
#
# TLS: Cloudflare proxies both names (orange cloud) and terminates public
# TLS at the edge with its Universal SSL wildcard. The cert referenced here
# is a Cloudflare Origin CA certificate for `finite.chat, *.finite.chat`
# (SSL/TLS -> Origin Server -> Create Certificate), so the zone runs in
# Full (strict) mode. No ACME, no DNS plugin, no API token on the box.
#
# Both blocks proxy to the same finitesitesd process; it splits the API
# plane from the site plane by Host header itself.

api.finite.chat {
	tls /etc/finite-saas/certs/finite-chat-origin.pem /etc/finite-saas/certs/finite-chat-origin.key
	reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:8787
}

*.finite.chat {
	tls /etc/finite-saas/certs/finite-chat-origin.pem /etc/finite-saas/certs/finite-chat-origin.key
	reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:8787
}
